title: Microsoft Golf 3.0 with serial
description: It&#039;s a whole new ball game. The top-selling golf game for Windows is better than ever, with a lightning-fast Windows game engine, superior graphics, and a realistic feel from the texture of the fairways to the birds singing in the trees. The sweet spot feels a mile wide as you connect. Beautiful. The dramatic look and feel of Microsoft Golf version 3.0 is just the start: it runs faster, plays easier, and feels more realistic than ever. And with play this true-to-life from the tee-off down to the pin, you&#039;ll concentrate on your game instead of ours. Escaping tough shots unscathed would be difficult enough without Golf 3.0&#039;s improved control features. But when you add a little competition via the Multiplayer feature - or one of the tough new computer opponents - those stance, club, and swing adjustments may just make the difference. It all shows up on the scorecard.
